com.worksap.nlp.sudachi

インタフェース Dictionary

  • すべてのスーパーインタフェース:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable

    public interface Dictionary
extends java.lang.AutoCloseable
    A lexicon and a grammar for morphological analysis. This class requires a lot of memory. When using multiple analyzers, it is recommended to generate only one instance of this class, and generate multiple tokenizers.
    関連項目:
    DictionaryFactory, Tokenizer, AutoCloseable

    • メソッドの詳細

      • create

        Tokenizer create()
        Creates a tokenizer instance.
        戻り値:
        a tokenizer

      • close

        void close()
        定義:
        close インタフェース内 java.lang.AutoCloseable

      • getPartOfSpeechSize

        int getPartOfSpeechSize()
        Returns the number of types of part-of-speech. The IDs of part-of-speech are within the range of 0 to getPartOfSpeechSize() - 1.
        戻り値:
        the number of types of part-of-speech

      • getPartOfSpeechString

        java.util.List<java.lang.String> getPartOfSpeechString(short posId)
        Returns the array of strings of part-of-speech name. The name is divided into layers.
        パラメータ:
        posId - the ID of the part-of-speech
        戻り値:
        the list of strings of part-of-speech name
        例外:
        java.lang.IndexOutOfBoundsException - if posId is out of the range
